<T>__{dissolving to:}
<L>__{interior miami courtroom day (1970)}
<A>__{the "charges" are being read by the judge, distant, not of this world. the court is lit in southern gothic daylight, ghostly chiaroscuro, all colors bled. camera moving along the sweaty white faces of the six older jurors, all of them straight "silent majority"... past the prosecutor, his shadow cutting the jury box... onto jim bearded, smoking 2 packs a day, a deep racking cough, sitting with his elder attorney... ray, robbie, john, pamela, others in support are there in background. the trial is going down like a morphine dream, jim featured in diopter close up.}
